2020/11/16
perfectsweeper: commandline minesweeper with a lot of cool settings
tinysweeper: commandline minesweeper with only essential settings

I want to get my programming skillz up, and I like minesweeper, and I want to put my brain to use [make something].

(have you ever heard "Parachute" by YUNIP? if not, you should listen to it. From Mikgazer 1)

It's gonna be a command line program.
It will look like this

